- menu.c
  - M_Draw(): skip when != key_menu|key_bindingMenu
  - M_PushMenu(): set to key_menu to show it
- in_win.c
  - IN_Frame(): checks for key_console and [de]activates mouse when changed
- cl_ents.c
  - CL_ParseFrame() - set to key_game to hide console
- cl_scrn.c
  - SCR_RunConsole() - set to key_console to show it
  - SCR_DrawConsole() - DrawNotify() when key_game or key_message
  - SCR_UpdateScreen() - check for menu|forcemenu|console while cin playback to hide cin
- console.c
  - Con_ToggleConsole_f() - calls M_ForceMenuOff() and (?) set to key_console to show
- keys.c
  - CompleteMenuKey() - set to key_console when menu disappeared
  - CompleteMenuCallback() - similar
  - Key_Event() - check var for determining message destination

- M_ForceMenuOff() calls:
  - vid_menu.c
  - menu.c :: M_PopMenu() - when menu level = 0
